      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Acknowledging the possibility that some wounds may be long-term and legacy-ing can be a more honest approach. It's possible that the struggle is as much about coming to terms with your own limitations and uncertainties as it is about trying to fix or overcome them. This acceptance might not make the pain disappear, but it could bring a sense of relief and self-awareness that allows you to move forward in your own way.",
      "source": "target",
